---
import BaseHead from '../../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import HeaderEn from '../../../components/HeaderEn.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <BaseHead
    title="Spousal & Child Support Lawyer Ontario | Hidden Income · FRO | Miao He"
    description="Child support and spousal support in Ontario. Hidden income investigation, self-employment attribution, overseas income tracing, FRO enforcement. 647-930-6688."
  />
  <meta name="keywords" content="spousal support lawyer Ontario,child support lawyer Toronto,hidden income divorce Ontario,self employed support calculation,FRO enforcement lawyer,overseas income spousal support" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/en/family-law/support" />
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="zh" href="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/family-law/support" />
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/en/family-law/support" />
  <style>
    *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body{font-family:Georgia,serif;background:#0F0A04;color:#E8D5B0}a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
    .lang-bar{background:#1A1208;text-align:right;padding:.4rem 2rem;font-size:.8rem}.lang-bar a{color:#C8B99A;margin-left:1rem}.lang-bar a.active{color:#D4A853;font-weight:600}
    .page{max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 2rem}
    .breadcrumb{font-size:.78rem;color:#A89070;margin-bottom:2rem}.breadcrumb a{color:#D4A853}
    h1{font-size:2rem;color:#F5E6C8;margin-bottom:.5rem}
    .lead{color:#C8B99A;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:2rem}
    .card{background:#1A1208;border:1px solid #3A3020;border-radius:8px;padding:2rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
    .card h2{color:#D4A853;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;letter-spacing:.05em}
    .card p{color:#C8B99A;font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:.8rem}
    .card ul{list-style:none;padding:0}.card ul li{color:#C8B99A;font-size:.85rem;padding:.3rem 0 .3rem 1.2rem;position:relative}.card ul li::before{content:"·";position:absolute;left:0;color:#D4A853}
    .faq-item{border-bottom:1px solid #3A3020;padding:1rem 0}.faq-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
    .faq-q{color:#F5E6C8;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.4rem}
    .faq-a{color:#A89070;font-size:.83rem;line-height:1.7}
    .cta{text-align:center;padding:2rem}.cta h2{color:#D4A853;margin-bottom:1rem}
    .btn-primary{display:inline-block;background:#D4A853;color:#1A1208;padding:.75rem 2rem;border-radius:6px;font-weight:700;margin:.5rem}
    .btn-secondary{display:inline-block;border:1px solid #D4A853;color:#D4A853;padding:.75rem 2rem;border-radius:6px;margin:.5rem}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="lang-bar"><a href="/family-law/support">中文</a><a href="/en/family-law/support" class="active">EN</a></div>
  <HeaderEn />
  <div class="page">
    <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/en/">Home</a> › Family Law › Spousal & Child Support</div>
    <h1>Spousal & Child Support</h1>
    <p class="lead">Support calculations depend entirely on accurate income figures. We specialize in uncovering hidden income, tracing overseas earnings, and ensuring the right amount is paid — or received.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>WHAT WE HANDLE</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Child support — Federal Child Support Guidelines calculations</li>
        <li>Spousal support — SSAG range analysis</li>
        <li>Hidden income investigation</li>
        <li>Self-employment income attribution</li>
        <li>Overseas income tracing — including China</li>
        <li>FRO (Family Responsibility Office) enforcement</li>
        <li>Variation and termination of support orders</li>
        <li>Interim support motions</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</h2>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">My spouse is self-employed and claims low income. What can I do?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">Courts have the power to impute income to a self-employed spouse where their reported income does not reflect their true earning capacity. We use financial disclosure tools and forensic analysis to establish the actual income for support purposes.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">How is spousal support calculated in Ontario?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">Spousal support is calculated using the Spousal Support Advisory Guidelines (SSAG), which produce a range based on the incomes of both parties and the length of the relationship. The amount and duration depend on factors including economic disadvantage caused by the marriage.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">My ex is not paying support. What are my options?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">You can enforce through the Family Responsibility Office (FRO), which has broad powers including wage garnishment, driver's licence suspension, and passport denial. We can also bring a contempt motion directly to the court.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card cta">
      <h2>Book a Consultation</h2>
      <a href="tel:6479306688" class="btn-primary">📞 647-930-6688</a>
      <a href="mailto:miao@miaohelaw.ca" class="btn-secondary">Email Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Footer />
</body>
</html>
